snippet.title: Cardinal Quest Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit http://www.cardinalquest.com for more info!

Cardinal Quest 1.0 is now online!

This is the second trailer of Cardinal Quest, this time showing footage from the first public release - as you can see the game is much flashier than the prototype shown in the first trailer.
